listitem.para:
					"dioValue":   trigger occurs when state (0|1) is present on one of DIO1...8 digital input channel. /para>

Function parameters: p1 - DIO channel number in range 1...8, p2 - DIO state which which triggers AI scan start 




						mdaqAIScanTrigger("dioValue", 1, 0);

refsection.programlisting:

mdaqEncoderInit(1, 0);
mdaqAIScanInit(1, [-10,10], %F, 10000, 1)
mdaqAIScanTrigger("encoderValue", 1, 1000, 1);
data = mdaqAIScan(10000, 10);
plot(data);


mdaqEncoderInit(2, 0);
mdaqAIScanInit(1, [-10,10], %F, 10000, 1)
mdaqAIScanTrigger("encoderValue", 2, 0, 0);
data = mdaqAIScan(10000, 10);
plot(data);
